```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Patient as 환자
    participant AZ as AZ_COM01001M<br/>접수완료
    participant MR as MR_COM02001M<br/>수납화면
    participant CMD as PaymentCMD
    participant PC as PaymentPC
